					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I'm a little wary of just providing you a solution if this is for your degree work; surely you should be proving you know how to design something here?<br /><br />Anyway, here's a hint:<br />Use a 74'138. Connect /RD and /WR to A and B, and connect CPU A15..A13 (and optionally A12) to the other four inputs to be active when reading or writing from 0xA000 through (0xAFFF or 0xBFFF). Only two of the outputs will be useful.</div>

